/*+ NoHashJoin(tq2 t2) NoMergeJoin(q2 t2 tq2 u2 u1) NoMergeJoin(q2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 account) NoMergeJoin(account q2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 q1) NoNestLoop(account q1 q2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 s1) NoNestLoop(account q1 q2 s1 t2 tq2 u1 u2 t1) NoNestLoop(account q1 q2 s1 t1 t2 tq2 u1 u2 tq1) NoNestLoop(account q1 q2 s1 t1 t2 tq1 tq2 u1 u2 s2) */ select account.display_name
from tag_question AS tq2
inner join tag AS t2
on tq2.tag_id = t2.id AND t2.name = 'machine-learning'
inner join question AS q2
on tq2.question_id = q2.id
inner join so_user AS u2
on q2.owner_user_id = u2.id AND q2.site_id = u2.site_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on u1.account_id = u2.account_id
inner join account AS account
on account.id = u1.account_id
inner join question AS q1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join site AS s1
on q1.site_id = s1.site_id AND s1.site_name = 'stackoverflow'
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.site_id = s1.site_id AND t1.name = 'optimization'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.question_id = q1.id AND tq1.site_id = s1.site_id AND tq1.tag_id = t1.id
inner join site AS s2
on tq2.site_id = s2.site_id AND t2.site_id = s2.site_id AND q2.site_id = s2.site_id AND s2.site_name = 'stats';
